---INFO---
The program is an alpha / heavy-development phase, so if you want to use 
JBEdit you have to come close to the source and edit it by yourself!


---REQUIREMENTS---
-Apache server (Tested on Apache 2.0) with mod_rewrite!
-PHP
-FFMPEG, tested on:
# ffmpeg -version
